### task-09.outline
Task: 09
Title: Anthropic outbound adapter, factory, and config enum
Phase: 4
Route: full
Slice: Slice 5 (Anthropic Outbound)
Dependencies: 07 (ChatModelPort.stream())
Scope: Create AnthropicChatAdapter implementing ChatModelPort via @anthropic-ai/sdk. Implement complete() mapping canonical ChatRequest to Anthropic Messages API format (system as top-level param, messages as alternating user/assistant). Implement stream() using SDK streaming. Register the adapter in ChatAdapterFactory for provider.type === 'anthropic'. Extend JsonFileConfigAdapter provider schema from z.enum(['openai']) to z.enum(['openai', 'anthropic']). Create adapter unit test and modify factory test to cover anthropic branch.
Acceptance Criteria: AC-11 (partial — AnthropicChatAdapter + factory selection)
NFRs: NFR-1, NFR-3 (@anthropic-ai/sdk confined to AnthropicChatAdapter)
Gate Criteria: Phase 4 Gate 2 (adapter correctly maps canonical types without leaking Anthropic shapes to domain/app)
Files:
  - src/infrastructure/outbound/llm/anthropic-chat-adapter.ts (CREATE) — AnthropicChatAdapter implements ChatModelPort. Constructor(client: Anthropic). complete(): maps ChatRequest to client.messages.create() params — system as top-level, messages as alternating user/assistant ContentBlock[], max_tokens from options. Returns ChatResponse with content from first text block, TokenUsage from usage. stream(): uses client.messages.stream(), yields ChatStreamChunk instances (content_delta from text events, usage from finalMessage). AbortSignal forwarded.
  - src/infrastructure/outbound/llm/chat-adapter-factory.ts (MODIFY) — Add branch: if modelRef.provider === 'anthropic', create new Anthropic({ baseURL: modelRef.baseURL, apiKey: modelRef.apiKey }) and return new AnthropicChatAdapter(client). Import Anthropic from '@anthropic-ai/sdk' and AnthropicChatAdapter from local module.
  - src/infrastructure/outbound/config/json-file-config-adapter.ts (MODIFY) — Change providerSchema type field from z.enum(['openai']) to z.enum(['openai', 'anthropic']).
  - src/infrastructure/outbound/llm/anthropic-chat-adapter.test.ts (CREATE) — node:test suite: complete() request/response mapping, stream() chunk mapping, SDK error propagation, AbortSignal forwarding. Uses hand-written stubs for the Anthropic SDK client (no real API calls).
  - src/infrastructure/outbound/llm/chat-adapter-factory.test.ts (MODIFY) — Add test: ChatAdapterFactory.create() returns AnthropicChatAdapter for provider: 'anthropic' ModelRef.
